I'm now zeroing in on the simulated flow. My plan involves crafting a "Continue with Google" button within `AuthView.tsx`. This button will trigger a `handleGoogleLogin` function, which replicates network activity. The handler's critical job will be to produce a mock user profile, structured like a "google-user," matching the existing user model and simulating a successful sign-in, just like our email/password setup. For authenticity, I'll incorporate an inline SVG Google 'G' logo. I will then add a note about the considerations for actual implementation.


