I'm now integrating the Google icon component and styling the "Continue with Google" button. The button's appearance is critical; it will use a white background and a gray border to stand out. I am also planning on adding the inline Google SVG 'G' logo to match the visual design, and will render the Google login button. This UI element's styling is under constant refinement.

